# Predicting Aqueous Solubility with Machine Learning

This project builds machine learning models to predict **aqueous solubility (logS)** of small molecules using cheminformatics tools.

## Methods

* RDKit molecular processing
* Physicochemical descriptor generation
* Morgan fingerprint generation
* Random Forest regression

## Models

1. Descriptor-based QSAR model
2. Morgan fingerprint model

## Visualizations

* Feature importance analysis
* 3D molecular visualization of prediction outliers

## Dataset

Delaney solubility dataset from DeepChem.

## Tools

* Python
* RDKit
* Scikit-learn
* Py3Dmol
* Jupyter Notebook
